nodes.bodyText: There are 6 %s in FHIR_NAME and 7 params here.  Something is amis.
Ah looks like "store-id" and "fhir-id" were meant to be "FHIR store ID" and "FHIR Resource ID". You can delete "fhir-id" or "store-id" or combine them into "fhir-store-id".
Does the test check for this text in the output?
